  "detailed_description": "<h1>Coming soon - Grunn!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Kart kids is a chaotic racing game, up to 60 tiny karts race each other in the local neighbourhood!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206230/extras/f1d3c05c60510ad2f3c6058e822e17eb.poster.avif?t=1726497701\" width=630 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206230/extras/f1d3c05c60510ad2f3c6058e822e17eb.webm?t=1726497701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206230/extras/f1d3c05c60510ad2f3c6058e822e17eb.mp4?t=1726497701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10-30 minutes of playtime.<br></li><li> Race against a ton of other small karts!<br></li><li> Local multiplayer for up to 2 players.<br></li><li> Cool physics, soothing pastel colours.<br></li><li> Set the amount of karts and laps to your own liking.<br></li><li> The racers wear cool hats.</li></ul><br><strong>Controls</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Arrow keys to drive (WASD keys for player 2).<br></li><li> Arrow keys and Return key to navigate the menu.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206230/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1726497701\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
